Class Kanji

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.dev.yvgenijsharovskij.n5kanjiandkanjistoryquiz.kanjilist.Kanji

  • public class Kanji
extends java.lang.Object
    Represents the kanji info for each kanji in the kanjilist for the KanjiListFragment and / or KanjiFragment class(es).
    Every method in this class is public.
